:59px}<\/style><h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Ara\u00e7 Asans\u00f6r\u00fc<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-366b01b elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"366b01b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<style>\/*! elementor - v3.23.0 - 25-07-2024 *\/\n.elementor-widget-text-editor.elementor-drop-cap-view-stacked .elementor-drop-cap{background-color:#69727d;color:#fff}.elementor-widget-text-editor.elementor-drop-cap-view-framed .elementor-drop-cap{color:#69727d;border:3px solid;background-color:transparent}.elementor-widget-text-editor:not(.elementor-drop-cap-view-default) .elementor-drop-cap{margin-top:8px}.elementor-widget-text-editor:not(.elementor-drop-cap-view-default) .elementor-drop-cap-letter{width:1em;height:1em}.elementor-widget-text-editor .elementor-drop-cap{float:left;text-align:center;line-height:1;font-size:50px}.elementor-widget-text-editor .elementor-drop-cap-letter{display:inline-block}<\/style>\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bf9c117 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"bf9c117\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"><div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"><p>Ara\u00e7 asans\u00f6rleri, \u00f6zellikle \u00e7ok y\u00f6nl\u00fc ve fonksiyonel \u00fcr\u00fcnler olarak \u00f6ne \u00e7\u0131kan geli\u015fmi\u015f teknolojilerdir. End\u00fcstriyel ihtiya\u00e7lara yan\u0131t veren bu sistemler \u00f6zellikle otomotiv ve lojistik sekt\u00f6r\u00fcnde yayg\u0131n olarak kullan\u0131l\u0131r. Ta\u015f\u0131mac\u0131l\u0131k faaliyetlerinde son derece i\u015flevsel olarak fayda sa\u011flamaktad\u0131rlar. G\u00fc\u00e7l\u00fc makara ve hidrolik kollar\u0131 ile kullan\u0131m esnas\u0131nda y\u00fcksek a\u011f\u0131rl\u0131ktaki y\u00fcklere h\u0131zl\u0131 yan\u0131t verebildi\u011fi gibi \u00fcst d\u00fczey enerji tasarrufu da sunmaktad\u0131r. Bu do\u011frultuda hidrolik ara\u00e7 asans\u00f6r\u00fc sistemleri, \u00f6zellikle yo\u011fun kullan\u0131m alanlar\u0131nda uzun vadede son derece verimli ve maliyet odakl\u0131 kullan\u0131m avantajlar\u0131na sahiptir.<\/p><p>Bunun yan\u0131 s\u0131ra otoparklarda kullan\u0131labilecek bu sistem, \u00f6zellikle alan sorunu ya\u015fayan ya da katl\u0131 otoparklarda ara\u00e7lar\u0131n kolay bir \u015fekilde istiflenmesine, katlar aras\u0131nda ta\u015f\u0131nmas\u0131na da yard\u0131mc\u0131 olur.<\/p><p>Ta\u015f\u0131ma kapasitesi 2.500 kg ile 10.000 kg aras\u0131nda de\u011fi\u015fen ara\u00e7 asans\u00f6rleri, binalar\u0131n \u00fcst ve bodrum katlar\u0131n\u0131 otopark olarak kullanmaya olanak sa\u011flamakta; yol, rampa gibi alan kay\u0131plar\u0131n\u0131 binaya geri kazand\u0131rmaktad\u0131r. Asans\u00f6r kabini i\u00e7ine ara\u00e7 ile girildi\u011finde s\u00fcr\u00fcc\u00fcn\u00fcn arac\u0131ndan inmeden istedi\u011fi kata gitmesini sa\u011flayan buton sistemi sayesinde kullan\u0131c\u0131ya b\u00fcy\u00fck kullan\u0131m kolayl\u0131\u011f\u0131 sa\u011flanmaktad\u0131r.<\/p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-25a863f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"25a863f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"><div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"><ul><li>Ara\u00e7lar\u0131n; konut, i\u015fletme ve otoparklarda katlar aras\u0131 transferi i\u00e7in kullan\u0131lan, hidrolik ya\u011f bas\u0131nc\u0131 ile \u00e7al\u0131\u015fan sistemlerdir.<\/li><li>Hidrolik \u00fcnitenin uygulad\u0131\u011f\u0131 y\u00fcksek ya\u011f bas\u0131nc\u0131 ile hidrolik silindir ve zincir, platformun hareketini sa\u011flar.<\/li><li>Hidrolik \u00fcnite yaln\u0131zca yukar\u0131 y\u00f6nde \u00e7al\u0131\u015f\u0131r. A\u015fa\u011f\u0131 y\u00f6nde platform kendi a\u011f\u0131rl\u0131\u011f\u0131yla iner. B\u00f6ylelikle enerji tasarrufu sa\u011flan\u0131r.<\/li><li>Ara\u00e7 platformlar\u0131 2 ve 4 kolonlu olarak imal edilmektedir.<\/li><li>Elektrik kesintisi veya olas\u0131 bir ar\u0131zada platformu manuel olarak a\u015fa\u011f\u0131 indirmek m\u00fcmk\u00fcnd\u00fcr.<\/li><li>Platformlarda, hortum patlamas\u0131na kar\u015f\u0131 emniyeti sa\u011flayan hortum patlama valf\u0131 kullan\u0131lmaktad\u0131r.<\/li><li>A\u015f\u0131r\u0131 y\u00fcklemelerde bas\u0131n\u00e7 emniyet valf\u0131 ve a\u015f\u0131r\u0131 ak\u0131m koruma r\u00f6lesi, platformu durdurarak motorun ve sistemin zarar g\u00f6rmesini engellemektedir.<\/li><li>Platform h\u0131z\u0131 ta\u015f\u0131ma kapasitesine ba\u011fl\u0131 olarak 0,05 \u2013 0,15 m\/s aral\u0131\u011f\u0131nda belirlenebilmektedir.<\/li><li>Ara\u00e7 platformlar\u0131, zeminde \u00e7ukur gerektirmeyecek \u015fekilde tasarlanabilmektedir.<\/li><\/ul><\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d531020 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"d531020\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Ara\u00e7 Asans\u00f6r\u00fc Ara\u00e7 asans\u00f6rleri, \u00f6zellikle \u00e7ok y\u00f6nl\u00fc ve fonksiyonel \u00fcr\u00fcnler olarak \u00f6ne \u00e7\u0131kan geli\u015fmi\u015f teknolojilerdir. End\u00fcstriyel ihtiya\u00e7lara yan\u0131t veren bu sistemler \u00f6zellikle otomotiv ve lojistik sekt\u00f6r\u00fcnde yayg\u0131n olarak kullan\u0131l\u0131r. Ta\u015f\u0131mac\u0131l\u0131k faaliyetlerinde son derece i\u015flevsel olarak fayda sa\u011flamaktad\u0131rlar. G\u00fc\u00e7l\u00fc makara ve hidrolik kollar\u0131 ile kullan\u0131m esnas\u0131nda y\u00fcksek a\u011f\u0131rl\u0131ktaki y\u00fcklere h\u0131zl\u0131 yan\u0131t verebildi\u011fi gibi \u00fcst d\u00fczey enerji [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featur